2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper focuses on using an aerial robot to capture the video and estimate human pose and trajectory. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper uses machine learning techniques such as convolutional neural networks and dynamic classifier selection to improve the accuracy of the pose and trajectory estimation. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also possible as the paper uses machine learning techniques to improve the accuracy of the pose and trajectory estimation. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with processing video data to estimate human pose and trajectory.
